snippet.title: Decay of Logos - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
With your mystical Elk companion, explore a vast interconnected world and seek revenge upon those who destroyed your village. Learn more at: https://www.decayoflogos.com

Decay of Logos, developed by Amplify Creations and published digitally by Rising Star Games, will be available globally from autumn 2018 across all major gaming platforms.

PS4 - Xbox One - Switch - PC

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/RisingStarGames/
Twitter: https://www.instagram.com/risingstargames/
Instagram: https://twitter.com/risingstargames

https://www.risingstargames.com
